 What Youâ€™ll Do 
 
This position is for an AI/ML Scientist within the AI Corporate Group. We are looking for an experienced technical contributor to work independently or with an AI/ML Lead Scientist. You will investigate, build, and deploy AI/ML systems and explore conceptually new solutions in a fast-paced environment. You will be at the heart of a growing and exciting focus area for Stanley Black & Decker and work with variety of its business units (including security services, manufacturing, industrial equipment and engineering products, as well as other units) to apply artificial intelligence techniques to our most difficult problems. 
 
